OL,3,CMan charged with manslaughter after
OL,4,Cthree-year-old run over by tractor
OL,6,FA man has been charged with
OL,7,Fmanslaughter after a three-year-old
OL,8,Fboy was run over by a tractor.
OL,10,FAlbie Speakman was killed after being
OL,11,Fhit on farmland off Bentley Hall Road
OL,12,Fin Tottington, near Bury, on 16 July
OL,13,F2022. He died before he could be taken
OL,14,Fto hospital.
OL,16,FNeil Speakman, 38, has now been
OL,17,Fcharged with Gross Negligence
OL,18,FManslaughter, and has been bailed to
OL,19,Fappear at Manchester Magistrates Court
OL,20,Fon 16 April 2024.
