OL,6,FIn the days following Albie's death,
OL,7,Ffriends and family held a vigil in
OL,8,FRadcliffe in memory of the 'sunshine
OL,9,Fboy'. Mourners laid candles and
OL,10,Freleased balloons to mark his passing.
OL,12,FHis funeral took place at East
OL,13,FLancashire Crematorium, in Radcliffe
OL,14,Fwhere a horse-drawn carriage took
OL,15,FAlbie from Radcliffe town centre to
OL,16,Fthe crematorium, as people gathered
OL,17,Falong the route to pay their respects.
