OL,6,FPaying tribute to him, his mother Leah
OL,7,Fsaid: "Albie was an incredibly loving,
OL,8,Faffectionate and caring boy who just
OL,9,Fwanted everyone to be happy. He was so
OL,10,Fsensitive and wanted everyone to be
OL,11,Fok, especially the people that he
OL,12,Floved.
OL,14,F"We all love Albie so much more than
OL,15,Fwe can ever put into words `
OL,16,Fespecially his Nan and his 'Nanny-
OL,17,FNanny', as he would always call her.
