OL,6,F"I will miss absolutely everything
OL,7,Fabout Albie, his voice, his smile, the
OL,8,Fsmell of his skin and the feel of his
OL,9,Flittle hands on my face when he would
OL,10,Fsay 'I love you mummy girl'.
OL,12,F"I'll especially miss going on
OL,13,Fadventures with Albie, anywhere and
OL,14,Feverywhere we could have fun; nothing
OL,15,Fwill ever fill the whole that he has
OL,16,Fleft in our hearts, we are broken
OL,17,Fbeyond repair.
