OL,6,F"I always call him my little sunshine
OL,7,Fboy because he has brought so much
OL,8,Flight into my life and he is my little
OL,9,Fray of sunshine, and I don't want his
OL,10,Flife to end here, I need to carry on
OL,11,Fliving for him and take him with me
OL,12,Fwherever I go. We still have so many
OL,13,Fmore memories to make, Albie!
OL,15,F"I love him so much and I know he will
OL,16,Ffind his way back to me someday,
OL,17,Fsomehow, because we need each other.
OL,18,FUntil then I will look for him in
OL,19,Feverything I do and I will celebrate
OL,20,Fhis life.
